    <item>
      <title>德国放松欧盟财政规则的努力正在集中势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/germany-s-push-to-loosen-eu-fiscal-rules-is-gathering-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟正在朝着放松其财政规则，以允许在德国的掉头赢得了一些传统反对者的支持之后，允许更多的国防支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/germany-s-push-to-loosen-eu-fiscal-rules-is-gathering-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 13:20:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
